name: lattez_Rural Architecture Renovation/乡村建筑
description: This model is suitable for rural architecture with five styles of white walls and gray tiles、skeleton wall、red brick wall、wooden grille、rough stone wall. The effects can be triggered by trigger words. It can be combined with controlnet1.1 for photo repainting.
